  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <h1>Features</h1>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
      <li>Create a drop-box for <strong>receiving submissions</strong>.</li>
      <li><strong>Distribute submissions</strong> to reviewers.</li>
      <li>Create <strong>assessment rubrics</strong>.</li>
      <li>Annotate submissions with <strong>feedback</strong>.</li>
      <!--li>Send feedback to students by email.</li-->
    </ul>
  </div>
